* The section on "Deconstructing a URL" provides a clear and concise explanation of how to read and understand the structure of a URL.
* The section on "Using Postman to Explore an API" provides a step-by-step guide on how to use Postman to explore an API.
* The section on "Getting Data from the Chicago Crime Data API" provides a detailed example of how to use the Chicago crime data API to get data on violent crime in Chicago.

